        protected Map<Integer,GroupProcessor.ProcessorAssociation> m_inputPullableAssociations
        A map between numbers and processor associations. An element (m,(n,p)) of this map means that the m-th input of the group processor is in fact the n-th input of processor p

      • m_outputPushableAssociations

        protected Map<Integer,GroupProcessor.ProcessorAssociation> m_outputPushableAssociations
        A map between numbers and processor associations. An element (m,(n,p)) of this map means that the m-th output of the group processor is in fact the n-th output of processor p
